Below is the build pack. It is structured so you can hand pieces directly to Claude Code or Codex.

Two implementation constraints worth keeping: in Next.js App Router, interactive state like forms, local storage, and trackers should live in Client Components, while validation is worth centralising with schemas such as Zod so profile and log data stay typed and safe. ([Next.js][1])

