# 3) Core user stories

```text
- as a first-time puppy owner
  - I want to enter my puppy’s details
  - so I get a plan that feels specific to my dog, not generic

- as a stressed owner dealing with barking/biting/poor settling
  - I want quick behaviour guidance
  - so I know what to do right now

- as an owner trying to improve routines
  - I want to log naps, training, walks, enrichment, and issues
  - so I can see what is driving better or worse days

- as an owner of an apartment puppy / multi-dog household / non-crate-trained puppy
  - I want advice that fits my setup
  - so I am not forced into irrelevant crate-only or backyard-only guidance
```

