# 8) Recommendation formulas

## Daily targets

Keep this rule-based, not fake-precise.

```text
Base age-stage target:
- sleep range
- enrichment range
- training range
- physical range
- calm-work range

Then modify by:
- breed group
- energy profile
- home type
- issues
- previous 7-day pattern
```

## Example

```text
12–16 week retriever, apartment, barking + biting:
- mental target: medium-high
- physical target: moderate
- calm target: high
- priorities:
  - sniffing
  - settle
  - handling
  - bite redirection
- avoid:
  - late intense play
  - over-long walks
```

