# 10) Insights engine

## Goal

Turn logs into practical suggestions, not vanity charts.

## Logic

* detect “bad days”
* compare against average
* highlight repeated drivers

## Example bad day rules

```text
bad_day if any:
- barkingCount >= 4
- bitingLevel >= 4
- accidents >= 2
- pacingEpisodes >= 2
- ownerStress >= 4
```

## Example insights

```text
- barking is higher on days with low sniff minutes
- biting is higher on low-nap days
- settling improves when calm minutes > 20
- accidents increase when toilet intervals are longer
```

