# 12) Technical architecture

## Recommended stack

* Next.js App Router
* TypeScript
* Tailwind
* localStorage persistence for MVP
* Zod for schemas/validation
* small rules engine in `lib/rules`
* seeded JSON/TS content modules

Next.js App Router is a sensible fit here because you can keep mostly static/content-heavy screens as Server Components and isolate interactive trackers, onboarding flows, and local-storage-backed widgets inside Client Components. Zod is a strong fit for runtime validation plus static typing for profile and log payloads. ([Next.js][1])

