# 21) Suggested implementation notes

## Keep recommendation output structured

Do not generate giant free-text blobs.

Use output like:

```ts
type RecommendationBundle = {
  priorities: string[];
  activities: { title: string; duration: string; reason: string }[];
  warnings: string[];
  environmentChecklist: string[];
  issueActions: { issue: string; actions: string[] }[];
};
```

## Keep issue guides reusable

A barking guide should be reusable across breeds, then modified by context.

## Keep content in data files

Do not hardcode guidance strings deep inside components.

